>--type</span><span class=3D"token operator">=3D</span>LoadBalancer <span c=
lass=3D"token parameter variable">--port</span><span class=3D"token operato=
r">=3D</span><span class=3D"token number">8080</span>
</code></pre><div class=3D"toolbar"><div class=3D"toolbar-item"><button cla=
