yle=3D"background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webk=
it-text-size-adjust:none;" class=3D"language-shell"><code class=3D"language=
-shell" data-lang=3D"shell">kubectl get services balanced
</code></pre><div class=3D"toolbar"><div class=3D"toolbar-item"><button cla=
ss=3D"copy-to-clipboard-button" type=3D"button" data-copy-state=3D"copy"><s=
