ss=3D"copy-to-clipboard-button" type=3D"button" data-copy-state=3D"copy"><s=
pan>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></div><p>The following example cr=
eates simple echo-server services and an Ingress object to route to these s=
ervices.</p>
<div class=3D"highlight"><div class=3D"code-toolbar"><pre tabindex=3D"0" st=
yle=3D"background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webk=
it-text-size-adjust:none;" class=3D"language-shell"><code class=3D"language=
-shell" data-lang=3D"shell">kind: Pod
apiVersion: v1
metadata:
  name: foo-app
  labels:
    app: foo
spec:
  containers:
    - name: foo-app
      image: <span class=3D"token string">'kicbase/echo-server:1.0'</span>
---
kind: Service
apiVersion: v1
